                        <p><em>Y finalmente</em>, to those tired, I simply say, we canât afford to be. </p>
<p><em>Inshallah, venceremos,</em></p>
<p>Baligh ibn Antonio Lopez</p>
<p><em>Antonio Lopez is a Trinity senior.</em></p>

